These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, ritmeester, game
3 different games are played: chess, snooker, mah-jongg
City: boston, venice, edinburgh
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, dog
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, baking, reading
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, snowmobile, subway
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, amaryllis, balloon-flower
 1. the owner of the dog is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 3. the fonseca-smoker is the person traveling to venice##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 5. the person who growsdaisy is the owner of the hamster##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
 9. the person playing snooker is the game-smoker##1
10. the person playing chess is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar      | fonseca  | ritmeester   | game      |
| Game          | mah-jongg      | chess     | snooker     |
| City           | venice | edinburgh  | boston   |
| Pet   | hamster   | dog     | chinchilla  |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks      | baking      | reading      |
| Transport   | subway      | snowmobile    | airplane   |
| Flower         | daisy    | amaryllis | balloon-flower |

