.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, alhambra, tiparillo
There 3 different types of food: apple, papaya, cranberry
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, grey, yellow
3 different games are played: chess, scrabble, canasta
City: edinburgh, hannover, san-francisco
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, juice
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower, iris
 1. the person playing scrabble is in the middle##1
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is the person drinking tea##1
 3. the person who growssunflower is in the middle##1
 4. the alhambra-smoker is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 5. the person eating apple is on the far left##1
 6. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
 8. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 9. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
10. the person eating cranberry is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
11. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Cigar         | alhambra | tiparillo  | havana     |
| Food           | apple        | papaya | cranberry    |
| Color   | grey  | yellow    | coral    |
| Game   | canasta    | scrabble    | chess   |
| City           | san-francisco        | hannover    | edinburgh        |
| Beverage         | soy-milk     | tea  | juice     |
| Flower     | iris         | sunflower       | poppy |

