.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, january, april
City: rome, marseilles, nizza
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, aristoff, game
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, board-games, drawing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, gospel, punk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, water-polo, golf
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daisy, poppy
 1. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 5. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
10. the game-smoker is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Birthday      | april   | march         | january |
| City          | nizza  | marseilles        | rome    |
| Cigar           | siglo | aristoff  | game  |
| Hobby   | drawing | baking | board-games         |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | jazz       | punk        |
| Sport           | handball       | water-polo        | golf       |
| Flower     | poppy       | zinnia  | daisy       |

