.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, april, may
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, horse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, daffodil, tulip
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, train
City: san-francisco, liverpool, hamburg
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, ritmeester, davidoff
House: craftsman, futuristic, wooden
 1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the craftsman house is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 7. the futuristic house is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 8. the davidoff-smoker is in the middle##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
11. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |       3        |
| Birthday      | may   | june        | april           |
| Pet         | hedgehog | horse          | mouse      |
| Flower           | iris   | daffodil | tulip |
| Transport   | jet-ski  | bike       | train         |
| City   | liverpool    | hamburg          | san-francisco        |
| Cigar   | ritmeester  | davidoff        | montecristo     |
| House         | craftsman   | wooden         | futuristic       |

