.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-1-18::.
3 different games are played: chess, go, mah-jongg
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, coral, lilac
House: palace, wooden, craftsman
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, soul, electronic
City: edinburgh, hannover, nizza
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, dahlia, balloon-flower
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish, russian
 1. the turkish is the wooden house##1
 2. the person who growsdahlia is the wooden house##1
 3. the wooden house is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the russian##1
 6. the craftsman house is the person playing chess##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the palace house##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the turkish##1
 9. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
10. the person playing go is the person traveling to nizza##1
11. the fan of funk is on the left of the malaysian##1
12. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |      3      |
| Game      | chess       | mah-jongg      | go      |
| Color          | coral        | lilac | fuchsia   |
| House         | craftsman       | wooden    | palace  |
| Music-Genre           | electronic | funk     | soul    |
| City   | edinburgh       | hannover   | nizza |
| Flower         | balloon-flower        | dahlia   | tulip     |
| Nationality     | russian          | turkish       | malaysian         |

