The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, card-games, fishing
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, black, pink
3 different games are played: monopoly, chess, canasta
City: venice, rome, colone
 1. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
 2. the manager is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
 7. the person who likes pink is the person playing chess##1
 8. the person who likes pink is on the left of the freelancer##1
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the colonial house##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
