House: cape-cod, craftsman, palace
3 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, mah-jongg
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, bolivar, pall-mall
 1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 2. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 3. the sunflowercher is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the chef##1
 5. the craftsman house is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is the person playing bridge##1
 7. the bolivar-smoker is the person playing bridge##1
 8. the person traveling to london is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 9. the palace house is in the middle##1
10. the pall-mall-smoker is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
